---
---
<section class="about-mission">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="mission-grid">
      <div class="mission-content">
        <h2 class="section-title">The Mission</h2>
        <p>
          We believe that artificial intelligence is a powerful ally for creativity, but it often needs a 
          "design compass" to reach its full potential. <strong>NotebookLM Slide Styles</strong> serves as that bridge.
        </p>
        <p>
          Our goal is to provide a curated set of instructions (YAML prompts) that allow anyone—from students 
          to executives—to generate professional-grade slides without needing to be a designer.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="mission-image">
        <div class="glass-box">
          <span class="mono-label">DESIGN SYSTEM</span>
          <div class="box-line"></div>
          <div class="box-line short"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-mission {
    padding: var(--space-4xl) var(--space-lg);
  }
  .container {
    max-width: var(--max-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .mission-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-4xl);
    align-items: center;
  }
  .section-title {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }
  .mission-content p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }
  .mission-content strong {
    color: var(--color-text);
  }
  .mission-image {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .glass-box {
    width: 300px;
    height: 300px;
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: var(--space-2xl);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-card-hover);
    position: relative;
  }
  .mono-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    position: absolute;
    top: var(--space-xl);
    left: var(--space-xl);
  }
  .box-line {
    height: 2px;
    background: var(--color-text);
    width: 100%;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }
  .box-line.short {
    width: 60%;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .mission-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .mission-image {
      order: -1;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
    }
    .glass-box {
      width: 200px;
      height: 200px;
    }
  }
</style>
